{"lemma":"قَمْحَة","slug":"قَمْحَة","root":"ق.م.ح","root_slug":"ق-م-ح","root_link":"/words/roots/ق-م-ح","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":1},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n36176","n36177","n36180","n36181"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%82%D9%8E%D9%85%D9%92%D8%AD%D9%8E%D8%A9"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"wheat"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"From the root ق م ح (q m ḥ). Cognate with Aramaic קַמְחָא (qamḥā, “flour”), Hebrew קֶמַח (qémaḥ, “flour”), Ge'ez ቀምሕ (ḳämḥ, “vegetables; leguminous plant”), ቀምሐ (ḳämḥä, “to eat upon, to graze”), Ugaritic 𐎖𐎎𐎈 (qmḥ, “flour”)."},"ipa":["/qamħ/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n36176","headword_ar":"قَمِحَهُ","root":"qmH","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (S, A, L, K,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qamoHN","text_ar":"قَمْحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AqtmHhu","text_ar":"اقتمحهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, A, L, K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He ate it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"took it into his mouth,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K,) namely, meal of parched barley or wheat, &c., (S, A, L,) not bread nor dates nor the like, but only what is eaten in the manner termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saf~N","text_ar":"سَفٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (L,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"without moistening it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"kneading it with water &c.;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aisotaf~ahu","text_ar":"اِسْتَفَّهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he took it in the palm of his hand"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, L) ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and conveyed it"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to his mouth"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"licked it up."},{"kind":"text","text":"(L.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qumoHapF minohu","text_ar":"قُمْحَةً مِنْهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AiqotamaHotu","text_ar":"اِقْتَمَحْتُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I so ate a mouthful thereof,"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e. of what is eaten in the manner described above]. (A.) ―         -b2-  And ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AqtmHhu","text_ar":"اقتمحهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"likewise signifies, (L, K,) as also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qamiHahu","text_ar":"قَمِحَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (L,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He drank it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"namely, what is called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nabiy*","text_ar":"نَبِيذ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (L, K,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$araAb","text_ar":"شَرَاب"},{"kind":"text","text":"[app. as meaning wine], and water, and milk. (L.)       -A2-  And, from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qamiHahu","text_ar":"قَمِحَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifying as expl. above, you say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qamaHa Eani AlmaA='i","text_ar":"قَمَحَ عَنِ المَا=ءِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (A,) or [simply]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qamaHa","text_ar":"قَمَحَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, L, K,) with fet-h, (S,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (L,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qumuwHN","text_ar":"قُمُوحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, L, K;) as also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qamaha","text_ar":"قَمَهَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qumuwhN","text_ar":"قُمُوهٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (L;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qAmH","text_ar":"قامح","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (A, L,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muqaAmaHapN","text_ar":"مُقَامَحَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qimaAHN","text_ar":"قِمَاحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (A;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tqm~H","text_ar":"تقمّح","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"page_break","n":2561},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AnqmH","text_ar":"انقمح","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, L, K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a camel)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"raised his head"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from the water"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"at the watering-trough, and refused to drink,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"his thirst being satisfied,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by reason of loathing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the coldness of the water,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of some disease."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlA_ibilu","text_ar":"الاـِبِلُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaAmaHati","text_ar":"قَامَحَتِ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The camels came to the water and did not drink,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"but raised their heads,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by reason of disease,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of cold,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the coldness of the water,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"because their thirst was satisfied."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$ariba fataqam~aHa","text_ar":"شَرِبَ فَتَقَمَّحَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A@noqamaHa","text_ar":"ا@نْقَمَحَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He drank"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and raised his head and left drinking by reason of his thirst's being satisfied."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fulaAnN mina AlmaA='i","text_ar":"فُلَانٌ مِنَ المَا=ءِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tqm~H","text_ar":"تقمّح","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one drank water,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the water, with dislike,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"loathing."},{"kind":"text","text":"(AZ.) ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^a$orabu faA^ataqam~aHu","text_ar":"اَشْرَبُ فَاَتَقَمَّحُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", said by Umm-Zara, means (tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I drink"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and I satisfy my thirst until I am not able to drink more, so I raise my head like the"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"camel that is said to be"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muqaAmiH","text_ar":"مُقَامِح"},{"kind":"text","text":": (A, TA: *) Az says that"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alt~aqam~uHu","text_ar":"التَّقَمُّحُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"primarily relates to water, but is metaphorically used by her in relation to milk: she means that she satisfied her thirst with milk until she raised her head from drinking it like as does the camel when he dislikes drinking water: (TA:) or, as some relate her words, she said,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faA^ataqan~aHu","text_ar":"فَاَتَقَنَّحُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (A, TA, *) which [likewise] means, “ and I raise my head in consequence of the being satisfied with drinking. ” (A.) [See also art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qnH","text_ar":"قنح"},{"kind":"text","text":".] ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qamaHa","text_ar":"قَمَحَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qumuwHN","text_ar":"قُمُوحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", is also expl. by Lth as signifying"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a camel)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became very languid by reason of vehement thirst:"},{"kind":"text","text":"but accord. to Az, this is wrong. (L.)"}],"source_refs":["S","A","L","K","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n36177","headword_ar":"قمّحهُ","root":"qmH","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (A, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taqomiyHN","text_ar":"تَقْمِيحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He repelled him"},{"kind":"text","text":"(i. e. his companion, A)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with a small and paltry thing, in lieu of much that was due to him;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, K; *) like as the wronging commander does to him who engages with him in a warring, or warring and plundering, expedition, by doling to him the least, or meanest, thing, and choosing for himself in preference to him in the partition of the spoil. (A, TA.)"}],"source_refs":["A","K"]},{"entry_id":"n36180","headword_ar":"قَمْحَةٌ","root":"qmH","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see the next preceding paragraph."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n36181","headword_ar":"قُمْحَةٌ","root":"qmH","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A mouthful of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qamiyHap","text_ar":"قَمِيحَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.]: (S, K:) or, as more than one have said"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of water."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)       -A2-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alqum~aHaAnu","text_ar":"القُمَّحَانُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":["S","K"]}]}}